金融前CEO莊偉忠亦就事件發言，他在fb專頁形容《禁蒙面法》為「攬炒之作」，認為首次引用《緊急法》後，未來就有無限次的特事特辦，最終變成慣例。除了影響香港國際聲譽、亦有機會影響香港獨立關稅區地位、信用評級機構、投資信心等等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1570181944158&amp;issue=20191004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1570181944158%26issue%3D20191004&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=9b752a48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1570181944158%26issue%3D20191004&h=c64f0cf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1570181944158&amp;issue=20191004</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"知錯能改 善莫大焉 我地手足一向賞罰分明<br />\n全港各藍店紅店注意 管理層公開表示同政權黑警鄉黑割蓆者，或停止逼害抗爭義士者，可納入免裝修名單，此為Lv.1<br />\n支援抗爭義士者，包括配合抗爭行動行事、提供實質資源如容身之處、糧食、文具，可進一步納入黃色經濟圈，此為Lv.2<br />\n<br />\n做人做狗 自己決定"},{"pid":"11b92f2a5fe6d2b0838abc0b13fc3f5efbc6cfff","tid":1624413,"uid":25028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"咁人地都肯轉軚 就算係得把口都叫做好開始"},{"pid":"682b74e8a4a5f75c96e6838bdeb3c5dc20bb304a","tid":1624413,"uid":79059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"知錯能改善莫大焉"},{"pid":"0b538fa562dfd06d937c924a4e10f79447131dcb","tid":1624413,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64e4d20d219d3e97201da96c29848149539fe42","tid":1624413,"uid":6435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"唔使幫佢裝修<br />\n都唔使幫佢宣傳"},{"pid":"abc6957d963369bfeec51359b267f1c6538bee35","tid":1624413,"uid":97852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"明報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢係咪想洗底食人血饅頭<br />\n唔會杯葛但唔會支持"},{"pid":"4737f7b5f1f91834369041418cfb0cf856f791dd","